tton for adding items to list.\n• You will need one function for handling button click event.\nRania El-Sayed - Helwan University (FEHU)\n\n\nAssignment 01\n• Design\n• Feel free to use your own colors but make sure to use consistent \ncolors.\n• I provide you with a classic design to follow but feel free to make a \nmore elegant design with excessive features.\n• Add custom fonts to your app => follow this link:\n• https://docs.expo.dev/develop/user-interface/fonts/\nRania El-Sayed - Helwan University (FEHU)\n\n\nAssignment 01\n• Make a report that includes:\n• Color palette and Fonts used in your project.\n• Screenshots of your design including different \nactions and their results.\n• Upload the code on expo snack and attach the \nlink in GitHub repo with your name.\n• Make a small video (2min) showing your \nproject in runtime.\nRania El-Sayed - Helwan University (FEHU)\n\n\nAssignment 01\nRania El-Sayed - Helwan University (FEHU)\n\n"""\n'}], 'model': 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile', 'max_tokens': 1500, 'temperature': 0.2}}
